==逝世==

在與癌症抗爭數月<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/dw/news/bulletin_110419_01/Elisabeth_Sladen |title=Doctor Who - Elisabeth Sladen - News & Features |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2011-04-20 |archive-date=2011-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423052556/http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/dw/news/bulletin_110419_01/Elisabeth_Sladen |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBCnewsEnt">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-13137674|title=BBC News - Doctor Who actress Elisabeth Sladen dies|work=[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]|accessdate=19 April 2011|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605211342/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-13137674|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Tuesday, April 19 2011, 20:50 BST |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/s7/doctor-who/news/a315485/elisabeth-sladen-dies-aged-63.html |title=TV - News - Elisabeth Sladen dies, aged 63 |publisher=Digital Spy |date= |accessdate=2011-04-20}}</ref>後，斯萊登於2011年4月19日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/8464295/Elisabeth-Sladen.html |title=Telegraph Obituary |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202051031/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/8464295/Elisabeth-Sladen.html }}</ref>逝世。BBC1的《十點新聞》和Daily Mirror、The Sun、the Liverpool Echo的頭版報導了她的死訊。在她死後播出的《異世奇人》第六季的第一集"[[:en:The_Impossible_Astronaut|The Impossible Astronaut]]"開頭出現了紀念斯萊登的字幕，該集播出完後，一個特別節目''My Sarah Jane: A Tribute to Elisabeth Sladen''在[[CBBC|CBBC]]播出<ref name="BBCnewsEnt"/>。為紀念她，舊《異世奇人》故事[[:en:The_Hand_of_Fear|The Hand of Fear]]之後在bbc 4播出。BAFTA的上一年度逝世者影片片段中，最後顯示了斯萊登。

